properties.Name: Aisle
properties.Description: An Aisle is the space between storage devices that is used by material handlers for access.

Columns.Name: WarehouseId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Warehouse.

Columns.Name: AisleId
Columns.Description:
The unique identifier of an Aisle.

An Aisle is the space between storage devices that is used by material handlers for access.

Columns.Name: AreaId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Area.

Columns.Name: AisleName
Columns.Description:
The name of the Aisle.

Ex:
- Building B/Aisle 6

Columns.Name: AisleLocationXCoordinate
Columns.Description: The aisle x-coordinate on a grid of the warehouse.

Columns.Name: AisleLocationYCoordinate
Columns.Description: The aisle y-coordinate on a grid of the warehouse.

Columns.Name: AisleLocationZCoordinate
Columns.Description: The aisle z-coordinate on a grid of the warehouse.

Columns.Name: LocationGpsLongitudePosition
Columns.Description:
The location GPS position expressed in longitude.

Ex:
GPS Coordinates (Ex= 39 deg 58.589 min) - seconds are converted to decimal format.

Columns.Name: LocationGpsLatitudePosition
Columns.Description:
The location GPS position expressed in latitude.

Ex:
GPS Coordinates (Ex= 39 deg 58.589 min) - seconds are converted to decimal format.

Columns.Name: StorageLocationStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Storage Location.

Columns.Name: SecurityLevelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Item Security Level.
